---
import cake from '../assets/cake.png'
import { BlobBackground } from '../assets/icons'
---

<section
  class='m-auto flex h-screen max-w-6xl flex-col-reverse items-center justify-center px-4 pt-20 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-20 md:pt-0'
>
  <div
    class='absolute inset-0 -z-20 skew-y-12 overflow-hidden bg-principal md:translate-y-40 lg:translate-y-52 2xl:translate-y-72'
  >
  </div>

  <article class='flex flex-col gap-5'>
    <h1 class='text-2xl font-bold leading-snug md:text-5xl'>
      Disfruta de un <span class='text-secondary'>pastel</span> en una celebracion
      especial
    </h1>
    <p>
      En cada capa, en cada sabor, encontrarás la pasión que ponemos en nuestra
      repostería. Sumérgete en una experiencia única con nuestros pasteles
      artesanales.
    </p>
    <a
      href='#menu'
      class='w-min self-center rounded-full border border-gray-500 bg-secondary px-5 py-2 font-bold text-white transition-colors duration-500 ease-in-out hover:bg-transparent hover:text-secondary md:self-start'
      >Menu</a
    >
  </article>
  <div
    class='relative flex h-1/2 w-full justify-center md:mt-10 md:h-4/6 md:items-center'
  >
    <BlobBackground
      className='md:top-0 bottom-0 md:m-auto absolute md:justify-self-center self-center md:h-[140%] top-5 w-full h-full'
    />

    <img
      src={cake.src}
      alt='pastel de cumpleaños'
      class='z-10 mb-24 h-[80%] md:h-96'
    />
  </div>
</section>
